<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/53956368" target="_blank" data-id="13802569" data-za-element-name="Title">
JavaScript和PHP，哪个更难？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/53956368/answer/137930840">
