<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/53045668" target="_blank" data-id="13436884" data-za-element-name="Title">
为何如此多的前端吹捧ES6?
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/53045668/answer/133170332">
