<div class="zm-item-rich-text expandable js-collapse-body" data-resourceid="13436884" data-action="/answer/content" data-author-name="小爝" data-entry-url="/question/53045668/answer/133170332">

<textarea hidden class="content">泻药。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img data-rawwidth=&quot;750&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;1334&quot; src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-db1ff0138e1ab8fc94936e385d9946c2_b.png&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;750&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-db1ff0138e1ab8fc94936e385d9946c2_r.png&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img data-rawwidth=&quot;750&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;1334&quot; src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2b499ab4f36d3a0d7a0aacb87814e19f_b.png&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;750&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2b499ab4f36d3a0d7a0aacb87814e19f_r.png&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img data-rawwidth=&quot;750&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;1334&quot; src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-416fbcafb635597d9182db93e0765517_b.png&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;750&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-416fbcafb635597d9182db93e0765517_r.png&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img data-rawwidth=&quot;750&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;1334&quot; src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-feeb5cfb7bac6fc8e03bd95f9411f38a_b.png&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;750&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-feeb5cfb7bac6fc8e03bd95f9411f38a_r.png&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img data-rawwidth=&quot;750&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;1334&quot; src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d1a70f26da80d15caa31a81504864f04_b.png&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;750&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d1a70f26da80d15caa31a81504864f04_r.png&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img data-rawwidth=&quot;750&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;1334&quot; src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c928b106215ea1b6fe2054fd597fb113_b.png&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;75