<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/27246926" target="_blank" data-id="3081693" data-za-element-name="Title">
如何看待程序员不写注释？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/27246926/answer/36412647">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="9954956">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="36412647"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>111</a>
</div>

<div class="zm-votebar">
<button class="up ">
<i class="icon vote-arrow"></i>
<span class="count">111</span>
<span class="label sr-only">赞同</span>
</button>
<button class="down ">
<i class="icon vote-arrow"></i>
<span class="label sr-only">反对</span>
</button>
