<div class="feed-main">
<div class="content">
<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/21445727" target="_blank" data-id="758987" data-za-element-name="Title">
为什么 Web 前端开发不抛弃 HTML 和 CSS，用纯 JavaScript 开发？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/21445727/answer/18414786">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="2515862">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="18414786"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>110</a>
</div>

<div class="zm-votebar">
<button class="up ">
<i class="icon vote-arrow"></i>
<span class="count">110</span>
<span class="label sr-only">赞同</span>
