<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/20795043" target="_blank" data-id="498473" data-za-element-name="Title">
redis怎么做消息队列？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/20795043/answer/89077346">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="31065880">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="89077346"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>110</a>
</div>

