<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/27078280" target="_blank" data-id="3014280" data-za-element-name="Title">
如何看待 HTML5 开源游戏引擎 Egret，HTML5 游戏开发的前景如何？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/27078280/answer/35829745">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="9720766">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="35829745"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
