<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/53705450" target="_blank" data-id="13702017" data-za-element-name="Title">
如何正确地总结 2016 前端技术？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/53705450/answer/136294876">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="50041345">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="136294876"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>110</a>
</div>

<div class="zm-votebar">
<button class="up ">
<i class="icon vote-arrow"></i>
