<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/49884331" target="_blank" data-id="12170410" data-za-element-name="Title">
为什么vue的更新记录不能有中文，中文文档也一直滞后？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/49884331/answer/118453686">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="42867790">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="118453686"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>110</a>
</div>

