<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">

<span class="summary-wrapper">
<span class="author-link-line">

<a class="author-link"
data-hovercard="p$t$huxpro"
target="_blank" href="/people/huxpro"
>黄玄</a></span><span title="伪前端工程师" class="bio">
伪前端工程师
